    "long_instructions": "### Beats with Filters\r\n\r\nYou're going to create a backing track that uses effects to adjust how the tracks sound as they play\r\n\r\n- All tracks will play layered together\r\n- The beat and bass tracks won't change at all\r\n- The vocal and two lead tracks will change volume and delay to stand out at different times\r\n\r\n**Here's what each sound should do:**\r\n\r\n- **Beat & Bass:** Play a beat and bass track with no effects\r\n- **Vocals and Leads:** Add effects so the volume and delay changes for each track every 4 measures\r\n- No two sounds should be at full volume at the same time\r\n- Emphasize different sounds with delay effects!\r\n- Make sure the total loop lasts at least 24 measures!\r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/4c6fffce6f10bc0d6c68dbe7357107a7-image-1745275267635.png)\r\n\r\nListen to the example below - listen for when certain tracks \"stand out\" from others. \r\n\r\nUse Live Coding to change the tracks and listen to how the effects change the loop!\r\n\r\n",
    "exemplar_settings": {
      "playerEnabled": true,
